<DocsLayout
  title="Installation"
  description="Download and install RefleK's on your Windows PC."
  nextPage={{ slug: "first-setup", title: "First-Time Setup" }}
>
  <h2>Download</h2>
  <p>
    RefleK's is available for Windows. Download the latest version from our
    <a
      href="https://github.com/ARm8-2/refleks/releases/latest"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener">GitHub releases page</a
    >.
  </p>

  <p>You have two options:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Installer</strong> (<code
        >refleks-&lt;version&gt;-windows-amd64-installer.exe</code
      >) - Recommended for most users
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Portable ZIP</strong> (<code
        >refleks-&lt;version&gt;-windows-amd64-portable.zip</code
      >) - For portable use
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Install with the Installer</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Download the installer from the releases page</li>
    <li>Run the installer and follow the prompts</li>
    <li>RefleK's will be installed and a desktop shortcut created</li>
    <li>Launch RefleK's from the Start menu or desktop</li>
  </ol>

  <div class="image-container">
    <img
      src="/assets/images/sessions_overview_2.webp"
      alt="RefleK's main interface"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <h2>Portable Installation</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Download the portable ZIP from the releases page</li>
    <li>Extract the ZIP to any folder</li>
    <li>Run <code>refleks.exe</code> from the extracted folder</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>System Requirements</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Windows 10 or later (64-bit)</li>
    <li>KovaaK's installed via Steam</li>
    <li>WebView2 runtime (included in installer, or auto-downloaded)</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
